# Optional: list rule basenames (one per line) to omit from the Slack / employee-factory
# persona bundle. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# When to add excludes:
# - Index-only files whose content is duplicated by the full rules linked from them
#   (you already exclude alex-trigger and alex-factory via --compact).
# - alex-growth-levers.mdc — high-level map; every lever points to another file that is
#   fully inlined. Excluding saves tokens; keeping it gives the model a navigation summary.
#   Uncomment the next line to drop the map:
alex-growth-levers.mdc
